====== H6586: פָּשַׁע ======

===== Source =====

a primitive root (identical with through the idea of  );

===== Meaning =====

expansion to  break  away (from just authority), i.e.  trespass ,  apostatize ,  quarrel

===== Definitions =====

  - expansion
  - break
  - trespass
  - apostatize
  - quarrel

===== Usage =====

offend, rebel, revolt, transgress(-ion, -or).
